OL,4,G1130FA Place in the Sun
OL,5,     GPortugal's beautiful Silver
OL,6,     GCoast, is the place that Maria
OL,7,     Gand Jess love the most. They hunt
OL,8,     Gfor a home, with a fine-tooth
OL,9,     Gcomb. But will they be raising a
OL,10,     Gtoast? _WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G1235FA Place in the Sun
OL,12,     GChris and Jane are moving to
OL,13,     GFrance, to Lot-et-Garonne given
OL,14,     Ghalf the chance. With a 200k
OL,15,     Gbudget, will they find their
OL,16,     Gdream place? And a brand-new life
OL,17,     Gfor them to embrace?
OL,18,     G_WorldPoetryDay
