OL,4,G1340FA Place in the Sun
OL,5,     GClergyman Ken wants a fresh new
OL,6,     Gstart; Larnaca in Cyprus has
OL,7,     Gstolen his heart. Five fab
OL,8,     Gproperties; how will they fare?
OL,9,     GAnd will any be the answer to
OL,10,     GKen's prayer? _WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G1440FCome Dine with Me
OL,12,     GThe competition takes place in
OL,13,     GLeeds, where Alice sows her
OL,14,     Gdinner party seeds. Can she win
OL,15,     Gher guests over with a ginormous
OL,16,     Gpavlova, and get the big score
OL,17,     Gshe needs? _WorldPoetryDay
