OL,4,G1515FCome Dine with Me
OL,5,     GNight two in Leeds and Andy's up
OL,6,     Gnext; will his posh nosh leave
OL,7,     Ghis guests perplexed? Fancy food,
OL,8,     Ga Ferrari and cocktail making;
OL,9,     Gwill he get good scores or a rude
OL,10,     Gawakening? _WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G1550FCome Dine with Me
OL,12,     GThird host in Leeds is student
OL,13,     GDanielle; will her guests be in
OL,14,     Gfood heaven or hell? After
OL,15,     Gserving dessert in her wedding
OL,16,     Gdress, one guest's proposal turns
OL,17,     Ginto a right mess. _WorldPoetryDay
