OL,4,G1620FCome Dine with Me
OL,5,     GThe fourth host in Leeds is Matt,
OL,6,     Gwho seems to impress off the bat.
OL,7,     GBut not everyone's happy, for
OL,8,     Gsome it's quite crappy, and
OL,9,     Gdessert ends up going splat!
OL,10,     G_WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G1650FCome Dine with Me
OL,12,     GLast host in Leeds is jeweller
OL,13,     GLynne, who hopes her night
OL,14,     Gsparkles, but can she win? With
OL,15,     Gdinner done, it's karaoke galore;
OL,16,     Gonly one can triumph, who has the
OL,17,     Gtop score? _WorldPoetryDay
