OL,4,G1825FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GTo Portsonachan Hotel & Lodges
OL,6,     Gthe B&Bers go, with a keen eye
OL,7,     Gfor detail and dust in tow. They
OL,8,     Gvisit Inveraray Castle on a
OL,9,     Gspooky trail, but will breakfast
OL,10,     Gbe an epic fail? _WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G1855FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GThere once was a flight attendant
OL,13,     Gcalled Meg, who decided to run a
OL,14,     GB&B instead. When her guests came
OL,15,     Gto stay, at her place - Lamlash
OL,16,     GBay, did she put the competition
OL,17,     Gto bed? _WorldPoetryDay
