OL,4,G2305F999: On the Front Line
OL,5,     GHurt head and breathless, and not
OL,6,     Gfeeling pain always, the
OL,7,     Gambulance comes. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,8,G0010F999: On the Front Line
OL,9,     GParamedics treat a man having an
OL,10,     Ganaphylactic reaction, a patient
OL,11,     Gwho's having a heart attack and a
OL,12,     Gman receiving chemotherapy who
OL,13,     Gmay have developed sepsis.
OL,14,G0115F24 Hours in A&E
OL,15,     GGary, 47, has been flown to
OL,16,     GKing's by air ambulance after his
OL,17,     Gmotorbike hit a car. Steve, 69,
OL,18,     Ghas got a fish bone stuck in his
OL,19,     Gfinger while trying to impress a
OL,20,     Gfemale friend.
